---
title: Mediterranean Gnocchi with Bocconcini and Oregano
description: Gnocchi gets a Grecian makeover! Pan-fried gnocchi are tossed with olives, salty feta, tomatoes, spinach and fresh bocconcini for a delicious combination of Italian and Greek flavours!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/gnocchis-a-la-mediterraneenne-4a5b1502.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/mediterranean-gnocchi-6241b22ca99b0f706458b1d0-c14c61df.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipes/mediterranean-gnocchi-6241b22ca99b0f706458b1d0
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
cuisine: Mediterranean
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 840 kcal
